Skullkickers (000 - 030) (2010 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Fawkes+JK-Empire) 



SKULLKICKERS is a fantasy action-comedy: Two mercenaries entangled in a high class assassination plot and nothing - werewolves, skeletons or black magic - will stop them from getting paid.

Following a hiatus, Skullkickers was continued in 2013 as Uncanny Skullkickers (#19), Savage Skullkickers (#20), Mighty Skullkickers (#21), The All-New Secret Skullkickers (#22), Dark Skullkickers Dark (#23) before resuming the legacy numbering with Skullkickers #24.
